premise_source_doc_sentence: Sade  (  singer  )   (  Helen Folasade Adu , OBE  )  , a British Nigerian musician and eponymous lead singer of the band

Helen Folasade Adu , OBE  (  Fọláṣadé Adú -LSB- fɔ̄láʃādé ādú -RSB- born 16 January 1959  )  , known professionally as Sade Adu or simply Sade  (  -LSB- ʃɑːˈdeɪ -RSB-  )  , is a Nigerian-born British singer-songwriter , composer , arranger , and record producer .
